title: Snipaste 1.8.3 Portable
description:
Simple But Powerful Snipping Tool


Download, unzip and use.  It is free and portable.  Enjoy.  I just love portable software.



Snipaste is a simple but powerful snipping tool, that also allows you to capture an area of your desktop and save it to file, copy it to the clipboard or to pin the screenshot back onto your screen as a floating window.
These floating window(s) can be zoomed, rotated, made translucent, and even made click-through, allowing you to keep them on your desktop as visual reference.
The program offers several editing options, including text, highlighter, arrows, mosaic blur, pencil and shapes that you can use to annotate your screenshot before saving it.
Other features include auto-detection of UI elements and windows, image scaling, capture groups, a built-in color picker, support for multiple screens, and more.


Publisher    Snipaste	
Price	Free
Version	1.8.3  
Last updated	Oct 03, 2016
File Size	8.47 Mb	
Requirements	None
